INSERT INTO WORDS VALUES ('lump', '[^럼p]\n덩어리, 각설탕, 혹, 부스럼, 다수, 수많음\n덩어리가 된, 한꺼번의, 일시불의\n일괄적으로 취급하다\n~을 참다, 견디다', 'A lump of something is a solid piece of it.\nA lump on or in someone''s body is a small, hard swelling that has been caused by an injury or an illness.\nAnnie picked up the tiny lump.\n', 0, '2016-11-09');
INSERT INTO WORDS VALUES ('lump it', '(달리 어쩔수가 없으므로) 받아 들이다', 'accept something unpleasant because there is no other choice', 0, '2016-08-31');
INSERT INTO WORDS VALUES ('lump sugar', '각설탕', '', 0, '2016-08-31');
INSERT INTO WORDS VALUES ('lumpy', '[럼픠]\n덩어리/응어리가 많은, 혹투성이의', 'Something that is lumpy contains lumps or is covered with lumps.\n', 0, '2016-08-31');
INSERT INTO WORDS VALUES ('lumpy face', '두툴두툴한 표면', '', 0, '2016-08-31');
