INSERT INTO WORDS VALUES ('society', '[쏘^싸이어뤼]\n(공동체를 이루는 일반적인) 사회, \n(특정한) 집단, 협회, 단체\n상류사회, 사교계', 'Society is people in general, thought of as a large organized group.\nA society is the people who live in a country or region, their organizations, and their way of life.\nA society is an organization for people who have the same interest or aim.\nSociety is the rich, fashionable people in a particular place who meet on social occasions.\nThis includes trying to improve my language skills. We live in a global society, so it is useful to speak another language.\n', 0, '2016-11-23');
INSERT INTO WORDS VALUES ('sock', '[싸악]\n양말 (복수형)\n(특히 주먹으로 치는) 강타\n세게 치다, 강타하다', 'Socks are pieces of clothing which cover your foot and ankle and are worn inside shoes.\n', 0, '2016-08-31');
INSERT INTO WORDS VALUES ('sock in', '(안개 따위가) (활주로)를 뒤덮다,\n(악천후로) (공항, 비행기) 를 비행불능케 하다', '', 0, '2016-08-31');
